{"tid":1300439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日新疆，明日香港】前車可鑑！又監控燈柱又信用評分，搞個遊行集會針對政府啲鬼祟維穩工程好無？！","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:13:01.000Z","uid":36640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aae0067792816188b3662248b5a599b186fed829","tid":1300439,"uid":36640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>（借人ac 開po）</strong><br />\n<br />\n「今日<del>新疆</del>，明日香港」 正名返先，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">東突厥</span></strong>呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/pqveZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FpqveZc.jpg&h=4c47a1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林奠又出嚟開記招講廢話，<br />\n一邊拖延香港局勢，一邊準備社會維穩工程。<br />\n中共今日處理香港嘅手法，同當年對東突厥根本一撚模一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n監控市民方面：<br />\n先係用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">監控燈柱</span></strong>大規模監控市民生活日常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">補充閱讀：[集思廣益] 智慧燈柱關注 持續更新 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298190/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298190/</a></span><br />\n再嚟個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">信用評級</span></strong>扣你班連登仔200分 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">補充閱讀：急! 突發，3年內將引入「社會信用評分系統」。文宣組幫幫手<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298213</a></span><br />\n想出境移民都走唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下再捉曬你班反動派香港人入集中營<br />\n一邊唱起來不願做奴隸的人們，一邊做奴隸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府方面：<br />\n香港警察戰術訓練隊 往新疆交流戰術理念 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/783/chi/n04.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F783%2Fchi%2Fn04.htm&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7BOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=6f72d678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/783/chi/n04.htm</a><br />\n李家超話東突厥嘅反恐工作值得香港作為參考 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287276</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今時今日香港人係中國只有兩個盟友：圖博同東突厥斯坦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n東突厥依家點？<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">「再教育營」關押的人數已達到百萬規模，超過二戰時期德國集中營關押猶太人的集中營關押猶太人的最高峰值70萬人。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">BBC 專訪東突厥「再教育營」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v8zNPmBttAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv8zNPmBttAQ&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7BOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=6f6a68b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v8zNPmBttAQ</a></span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府在新疆全境進行各種監控，禁止在學校教授維吾爾族語言，拆毀維族歷史建築等。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">紐約時報於東突厥實地採訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2019/04/04/world/asia/xinjiang-china-surveillance-prison.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2019%2F04%2F04%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fxinjiang-china-surveillance-prison.html&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7BOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=0c4926b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2019/04/04/world/asia/xinjiang-china-surveillance-prison.html</a> </span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">2009年維族記者、作家海萊提&middot;尼亞孜（Gheyret Niyaz）被捕，後被烏魯木齊中級法院以「洩露國家秘密」罪判刑15年。至今接近400名維族知識精英被拘押、失蹤、監禁，包括 101 名學⽣和 285 名學者、藝⼈和記者。</span><br />\n<br />\n維族一直都有係世界各地聲援香港，<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/3SJjNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2F3SJjNV.jpg&h=5770d5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人亦都無忘記過維族人嘅慘況嫁！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/AEBmQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FAEBmQj.jpg&h=97f965b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/lawFb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FlawFb1.jpg&h=89eca24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年係東突厥斯坦7.15 事件十週年，全球13個國家21個城市都有聲援維吾爾族人嘅活動。維族朋友托我表示，希望香港都可以有聲援活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/zjEYvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FzjEYvS.jpg&h=29dde341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為免整場反送中運動失焦，不如我地藉呢個機會整合一下港共嘅維穩工程，提出「反送中」嘅核心思想係反對政府試圖濛糊港中邊界、漠視一國兩制！並以東突厥斯坦嘅現況為鑑，準備大量文宣向仲未清楚信用評級同監控燈柱嘅市民宣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>內容</strong><br />\n1. 重申反送中運動五大訴求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 提出反送中運動嘅核心思想係反對政府試圖濛糊港中邊界、打壓港人自治 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 政府維穩工程合集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dress code</strong><br />\n著返代表東突厥嘅淺藍色/淺色牛仔？<br />\n不過香港人鍾意買衫，隨身有多幾件唔同嘅衫都唔出奇丫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲有無其他意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無學界嘅朋友同埋其他組織者可以一齊幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719f886d590492f1d5282c04d5a1997d02a5e1e2","tid":1300439,"uid":179535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}